ffset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Neurotoxins</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Soften expression lines, natural finish.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Skinvive</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Micro-injections for lasting hydration and smoothness.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Skincare</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Medical-grade routines to maintain results.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Teeth Whitening</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Brighter smiles, safely.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Filler Dissolving</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Refine or correct prior filler with hyaluronidase.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Juvederm Fillers</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Restore volume and definition.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Smooth PDO Threads</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Stimulate collagen with minimally invasive threads.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Microneedling</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Improve texture, pores, and scars.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Aerolase</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Gentle laser for acne, pigment, redness, rejuvenation.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold">Chemical Peels</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Even tone and refine texture.</p><a class="mt-3 inline-block text-sm underline underline-offset-4" href="#contact">Book</a></div>
</section>
<section id="contact" class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Contact</h2>
  <p class="text-white/70 mt-2">Email: info@dessencewellness.com • Phone: (000) 000-0000</p>
</section>
</Layout>
